channel.title: Ignation.org - Can the feds shut you down?
channel.description:
I was looking into a few things and I saw this post on ignation.org about megaupload being terminated check it out!
[url=http://www.weareig.org/showthread.php?24-SOPA-sponsor-has-another-Internet-bill-that-records-you-24-7]lol, google, no click here. I wish I was google... Ide have more money than you<3[/url]
I think the filter erked my chain :P
Whats your thought?
